  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=fbaf6f6f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2Fg0kpxARkI2Q4iaUezFK8JM4H01TRaENBfePjDctnzkXgMpJsVX28IOVFolF3qljMb5a6yVgZfiaa4bUWIk5YQpzA%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <div data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" data-website=\"https://www.mdnice.com\" style=\"padding:10px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6em;overflow-wrap:break-word;word-spacing:0em;word-break:break-word;background:no-repeat;width:auto;font-family:&quot;SF Pro SC&quot;, &quot;HanHei SC&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;Myriad Set Pro&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, &quot;Apple Legacy Chevron&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:left;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <blockquote style=\"margin: 20px 0px;border-style: none none none solid;border-width: 3px 3px 3px 5px;border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) rgb(231, 142, 52);background: rgb(255, 249, 243) no-repeat;width: auto;height: auto;box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px 0px;display: block;overflow: auto;border-radius: 5px;padding: 18px 21px;\">\n    <p style=\"padding:8px 0px;word-spacing:0.1em;margin:0px;text-indent:0em;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"border-radius:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;font-weight:bold;background:no-repeat;width:auto;border-width:3px;border-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-style:none;height:auto;\"><span leaf=\"\">导语：</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;为什么你玩 AI 绘画坚持不到三天就想卸载？不是你没艺术细胞，而是你还没掌握那套能让 AI “听话”的黑话。</span></p>\n   </blockquote>\n   <hr style=\"border-radius: 0px;background: linear-gradient(to right, rgba(248, 57, 41, 0), rgb(244, 138, 0), rgba(248, 57, 41, 0)) no-repeat;width: auto;height: 2px;padding: 0px;margin: 20px 0px;border-width: initial;border-style: none;border-color: initial;border-image: initial;text-align: center;\">\n   <h3 data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin: 30px 0px 5px;padding: 0px;display: block;text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;color: rgb(231, 142, 52);letter-spacing: 0em;text-align: left;font-weight: bold;display: inline-block;\"><span leaf=\"\">一、 为什么你的 AI 总是“人工智障”？</span></span></h3>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding:8px 0px;margin:5px 0px;word-spacing:0.1em;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:16px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">很多人初试 Midjourney 或 Stable Diffusion 时，习惯输入简单的词汇。比如想画个美女，直接输入&nbsp;</span><code style=\"letter-spacing: 0em;background: rgb(255, 246, 237) no-repeat;width: auto;height: auto;border-style: none;border-width: 3px;border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0) rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);color: rgb(231, 142, 52);font-size: 15px;overflow-wrap: break-word;padding: 2px 4px;border-radius: 3px;margin: 0px 2px;font-family: &quot;Operator Mono&quot;, Consolas, Monaco, Menlo, monospace;word-break: break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\">beautiful girl</span></code><span leaf=\"\">。</span></p>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding:8px 0px;margin:5px 0px;word-spacing:0.1em;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:16px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">结果呢？出来的往往是千篇一律的“网红脸”，生硬、塑料感重、毫无灵魂。</span></p>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding:8px 0px;margin:5px 0px;word-spacing:0.1em;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:16px;text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"border-radius:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;font-weight:bold;background:no-repeat;width:auto;border-width:3px;border-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-style:none;height:auto;\"><span leaf=\"\">AI 绘画的核心秘诀在于：权重关键词。</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;真正的高手，从不指望 AI 的随机发挥，而是通过专业的</span><strong style=\"border-radius:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;font-weight:bold;background:no-repeat;width:auto;border-width:3px;border-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-style:none;height:auto;\"><span leaf=\"\">摄影术语、渲染引擎逻辑、光影控制</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">来精准引导。当你学会把&nbsp;</span><code style=\"letter-spacing: 0em;background: rgb(255, 246, 237) no-repeat;width: auto;height: auto;border-style: none;border-width: 3px;border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0) rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);color: rgb(231, 142, 52);font-size: 15px;overflow-wrap: break-word;padding: 2px 4px;border-radius: 3px;margin: 0px 2px;font-family: &quot;Operator Mono&quot;, Consolas, Monaco, Menlo, monospace;word-break: break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\">beautiful girl</span></code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;升级为配合&nbsp;</span><code style=\"letter-spacing: 0em;background: rgb(255, 246, 237) no-repeat;width: auto;height: auto;border-style: none;border-width: 3px;border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0) rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);color: rgb(231, 142, 52);font-size: 15px;overflow-wrap: break-word;padding: 2px 4px;border-radius: 3px;margin: 0px 2px;font-family: &quot;Operator Mono&quot;, Consolas, Monaco, Menlo, monospace;word-break: break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\">volumetric lighting</span></code><span leaf=\"\">（体积光）和&nbsp;</span><code style=\"letter-spacing: 0em;background: rgb(255, 246, 237) no-repeat;width: auto;height: auto;border-style: none;border-width: 3px;border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0) rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);color: rgb(231, 142, 52);font-size: 15px;overflow-wrap: break-word;padding: 2px 4px;border-radius: 3px;margin: 0px 2px;font-family: &quot;Operator Mono&quot;, Consolas, Monaco, Menlo, monospace;word-break: break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\">Rim light</span></code><span leaf=\"\">（轮廓光）的组合拳时，画面的质感将瞬间从“地摊货”变成“大片”。</span></p>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding:8px 0px;margin:5px 0px;word-spacing:0.1em;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:16px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">为了帮大家跨越新手期，我梳理了这套涵盖光影、画质、构图、风格、材质五个维度的</span><strong style=\"border-radius:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;font-weight:bold;background:no-repeat;width:auto;border-width:3px;border-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-style:none;height:auto;\"><span leaf=\"\">50个核心指令集</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">。</span></p>\n   <hr style=\"border-radius: 0px;background: linear-gradient(to right, rgba(248, 57, 41, 0), rgb(244, 138, 0), rgba(248, 57, 41, 0)) no-repeat;width: auto;height: 2px;padding: 0px;margin: 20px 0px;border-width: initial;border-style: none;border-color: initial;border-image: initial;text-align: center;\">\n   <h3 data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin: 30px 0px 5px;padding: 0px;display: block;text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;color: rgb(231, 142, 52);letter-spacing: 0em;text-align: left;font-weight: bold;display: inline-block;\"><span leaf=\"\">二、 核心指令集：从入门到进阶的“魔法口令”</span></span></h3>\n   <h4 data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin: 5px 0px;padding: 0px;display: block;text-align: left;font-weight: bold;font-size: 15px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(231, 142, 52);letter-spacing: 0em;text-align: left;font-weight: bold;display: inline-block;\"><span leaf=\"\">1. 光影与氛围（赋予画面灵魂）</span></span></h4>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding:8px 0px;margin:5px 0px;word-spacing:0.1em;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:16px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">光影是画面的生命线。掌握这些词，你就能控制画面的“情绪”。</span></p>\n   <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;margin: 8px 0px;padding: 0px 0px 0px 20px;color: rgb(231, 142, 52);font-size: 15px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"word-spacing:0.1em;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"border-radius:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;font-weight:bold;background:no-repeat;width:auto;border-width:3px;border-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-style:none;height:auto;\"><span leaf=\"\">Cinematic lighting</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;- 电影级光照，营造大片叙事感</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"word-spacing:0.1em;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"border-radius:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;font-weight:bold;background:no-repeat;width:auto;border-width:3px;border-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-style:none;height:auto;\"><span leaf=\"\">Volumetric lighting</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;- 体积光/丁达尔效应，增加空间通透感</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"word-spacing:0.1em;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"border-radius:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;font-weight:bold;background:no-repeat;width:auto;border-width:3px;border-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-style:none;height:auto;\"><span leaf=\"\">Rim light</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;- 轮廓光，勾勒主体边缘，增强立体感</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"word-spacing:0.1em;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"border-radius:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;font-weight:bold;background:no-repeat;width:auto;border-width:3px;border-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-style:none;height:auto;\"><span leaf=\"\">Bioluminescence</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;- 生物荧光，适合奇幻或神秘夜景</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"word-spacing:0.1em;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"border-radius:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;font-weight:bold;background:no-repeat;width:auto;border-width:3px;border-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-style:none;height:auto;\"><span leaf=\"\">God rays</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;- 耶稣光，营造神圣或宏大的史诗氛围</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"word-spacing:0.1em;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"border-radius:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;font-weight:bold;background:no-repeat;width:auto;border-width:3px;border-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-style:none;height:auto;\"><span leaf=\"\">Soft illumination</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;- 柔和照明，适合细腻的人像或静物</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"word-spacing:0.1em;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"border-radius:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;font-weight:bold;background:no-repeat;width:auto;border-width:3px;border-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-style:none;height:auto;\"><span leaf=\"\">Neon ambiance</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;- 霓虹氛围，赛博朋克必备</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"word-spacing:0.1em;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"border-radius:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;font-weight:bold;background:no-repeat;width:auto;border-width:3px;border-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-style:none;height:auto;\"><span leaf=\"\">Chiaroscuro</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;- 明暗对照法，强烈的艺术对比</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"word-spacing:0.1em;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"border-radius:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;font-weight:bold;background:no-repeat;width:auto;border-width:3px;border-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-style:none;height:auto;\"><span leaf=\"\">Global illumination</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;- 全局光照，模拟真实的光线反射</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"word-spacing:0.1em;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"border-radius:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;font-weight:bold;background:no-repeat;width:auto;border-width:3px;border-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-style:none;height:auto;\"><span leaf=\"\">Moody lighting</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;- 情绪化打光，营造忧郁或神秘的氛围</span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <h4 data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin: 5px 0px;padding: 0px;display: block;text-align: left;font-weight: bold;font-size: 15px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(231, 142, 52);letter-spacing: 0em;text-align: left;font-weight: bold;display: inline-block;\"><span leaf=\"\">2. 画质与渲染（决定精细度上限）</span></span></h4>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding:8px 0px;margin:5px 0px;word-spacing:0.1em;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:16px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">不要只求画出来，要追求画得“贵”。</span></p>\n   <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;margin: 8px 0px;padding: 0px 0px 0px 20px;color: rgb(231, 142, 52);font-size: 15px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"word-spacing:0.1em;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"border-radius:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;font-weight:bold;background:no-repeat;width:auto;border-width:3px;border-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-style:none;height:auto;\"><span leaf=\"\">8k resolution</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;- 极致分辨率，增加细节密度</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"word-spacing:0.1em;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"border-radius:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;font-weight:bold;background:no-repeat;width:auto;border-width:3px;border-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-style:none;height:auto;\"><span leaf=\"\">Unreal Engine 5</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;- 虚幻引擎5渲染，追求3D大作质感</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"word-spacing:0.1em;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"border-radius:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;font-weight:bold;background:no-repeat;width:auto;border-width:3px;border-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-style:none;height:auto;\"><span leaf=\"\">Octane render</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;- OC渲染风格，光影效果极度逼真</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"word-spacing:0.1em;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"border-radius:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;font-weight:bold;background:no-repeat;width:auto;border-width:3px;border-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-style:none;height:auto;\"><span leaf=\"\">Hyper-realistic</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;- 超写实主义，媲美真实照片</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"word-spacing:0.1em;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"border-radius:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;font-weight:bold;background:no-repeat;width:auto;border-width:3px;border-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-style:none;height:auto;\"><span leaf=\"\">Highly detailed</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;- 强化画面内容的丰富度</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"word-spacing:0.1em;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"border-radius:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;font-weight:bold;background:no-repeat;width:auto;border-width:3px;border-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-style:none;height:auto;\"><span leaf=\"\">Sharp focus</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;- 锐利对焦，杜绝画面肉感</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"word-spacing:0.1em;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"border-radius:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;font-weight:bold;background:no-repeat;width:auto;border-width:3px;border-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-style:none;height:auto;\"><span leaf=\"\">Ray tracing</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;- 光线追踪，处理反射与折射的利器</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"word-spacing:0.1em;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"border-radius:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;font-weight:bold;background:no-repeat;width:auto;border-width:3px;border-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-style:none;height:auto;\"><span leaf=\"\">Intricate details</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;- 复杂的机械或纹理细节</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"word-spacing:0.1em;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"border-radius:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;font-weight:bold;background:no-repeat;width:auto;border-width:3px;border-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-style:none;height:auto;\"><span leaf=\"\">Masterpiece</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;- 杰作权重，全方位提升画质</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"word-spacing:0.1em;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"border-radius:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;font-weight:bold;background:no-repeat;width:auto;border-width:3px;border-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-style:none;height:auto;\"><span leaf=\"\">HDR</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;- 高动态范围，保留亮部与暗部的所有秘密</span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <h4 data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin: 5px 0px;padding: 0px;display: block;text-align: left;font-weight: bold;font-size: 15px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(231, 142, 52);letter-spacing: 0em;text-align: left;font-weight: bold;display: inline-block;\"><span leaf=\"\">3. 摄影与镜头（控制视觉叙事）</span></span></h4>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding:8px 0px;margin:5px 0px;word-spacing:0.1em;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:16px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">别让 AI 乱猜视角，你要做画面的“导演”。</span></p>\n   <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;margin: 8px 0px;padding: 0px 0px 0px 20px;color: rgb(231, 142, 52);font-size: 15px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"word-spacing:0.1em;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"border-radius:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;font-weight:bold;background:no-repeat;width:auto;border-width:3px;border-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-style:none;height:auto;\"><span leaf=\"\">Wide angle lens</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;- 广角镜头，容纳宏大的场景</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"word-spacing:0.1em;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"border-radius:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;font-weight:bold;background:no-repeat;width:auto;border-width:3px;border-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-style:none;height:auto;\"><span leaf=\"\">Macro shot</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;- 微距摄影，捕捉纹理与细节的震撼</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"word-spacing:0.1em;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"border-radius:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;font-weight:bold;background:no-repeat;width:auto;border-width:3px;border-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-style:none;height:auto;\"><span leaf=\"\">Bokeh</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;- 散景/背景虚化，让主体脱颖而出</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"word-spacing:0.1em;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"border-radius:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;font-weight:bold;background:no-repeat;width:auto;border-width:3px;border-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-style:none;height:auto;\"><span leaf=\"\">Depth of field</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;- 景深，拉开画面的纵深层次</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"word-spacing:0.1em;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"border-radius:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;font-weight:bold;background:no-repeat;width:auto;border-width:3px;border-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-style:none;height:auto;\"><span leaf=\"\">Fish-eye view</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;- 鱼眼视角，极具冲击力的视觉变形</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"word-spacing:0.1em;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"border-radius:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;font-weight:bold;background:no-repeat;width:auto;border-width:3px;border-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-style:none;height:auto;\"><span leaf=\"\">Low angle shot</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;- 低角度仰拍，展现力量感与高大感</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"word-spacing:0.1em;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"border-radius:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;font-weight:bold;background:no-repeat;width:auto;border-width:3px;border-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-style:none;height:auto;\"><span leaf=\"\">Bird's eye view</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;- 鸟瞰视角，掌控全局的上帝视角</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"word-spacing:0.1em;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"border-radius:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;font-weight:bold;background:no-repeat;width:auto;border-width:3px;border-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-style:none;height:auto;\"><span leaf=\"\">Dutch angle</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;- 荷兰位，营造动荡或悬疑的氛围</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"word-spacing:0.1em;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"border-radius:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;font-weight:bold;background:no-repeat;width:auto;border-width:3px;border-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-style:none;height:auto;\"><span leaf=\"\">Telephoto lens</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;- 长焦镜头，压缩空间感，适合专业人像</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"word-spacing:0.1em;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"border-radius:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;font-weight:bold;background:no-repeat;width:auto;border-width:3px;border-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-style:none;height:auto;\"><span leaf=\"\">Isometric view</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;- 等轴测视图，2.5D 游戏或插画常用</span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <h4 data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin: 5px 0px;padding: 0px;display: block;text-align: left;font-weight: bold;font-size: 15px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(231, 142, 52);letter-spacing: 0em;text-align: left;font-weight: bold;display: inline-block;\"><span leaf=\"\">4. 艺术风格（定调创作基调）</span></span></h4>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding:8px 0px;margin:5px 0px;word-spacing:0.1em;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:16px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">一句话改变整个世界的底色。</span></p>\n   <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;margin: 8px 0px;padding: 0px 0px 0px 20px;color: rgb(231, 142, 52);font-size: 15px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"word-spacing:0.1em;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"border-radius:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;font-weight:bold;background:no-repeat;width:auto;border-width:3px;border-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-style:none;height:auto;\"><span leaf=\"\">Cyberpunk style</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;- 赛博朋克，霓虹与高科技的碰撞</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"word-spacing:0.1em;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"border-radius:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;font-weight:bold;background:no-repeat;width:auto;border-width:3px;border-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-style:none;height:auto;\"><span leaf=\"\">Steampunk aesthetic</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;- 蒸汽朋克，黄铜与工业的浪漫</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"word-spacing:0.1em;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"border-radius:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;font-weight:bold;background:no-repeat;width:auto;border-width:3px;border-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-style:none;height:auto;\"><span leaf=\"\">Ukiyo-e style</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;- 浮世绘，极具东方韵味的线条感</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"word-spacing:0.1em;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"border-radius:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;font-weight:bold;background:no-repeat;width:auto;border-width:3px;border-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-style:none;height:auto;\"><span leaf=\"\">Oil painting</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;- 经典油画，厚重质感与艺术笔触</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"word-spacing:0.1em;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"border-radius:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;font-weight:bold;background:no-repeat;width:auto;border-width:3px;border-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-style:none;height:auto;\"><span leaf=\"\">Watercolor sketch</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;- 水彩速写，流动且清新的美感</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"word-spacing:0.1em;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"border-radius:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;font-weight:bold;background:no-repeat;width:auto;border-width:3px;border-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-style:none;height:auto;\"><span leaf=\"\">Concept art</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;- 概念草图，电影/游戏设定集风格</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"word-spacing:0.1em;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"border-radius:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;font-weight:bold;background:no-repeat;width:auto;border-width:3px;border-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-style:none;height:auto;\"><span leaf=\"\">Matte painting</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;- 接景绘画，宏大的史诗级背景</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"word-spacing:0.1em;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"border-radius:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;font-weight:bold;background:no-repeat;width:auto;border-width:3px;border-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-style:none;height:auto;\"><span leaf=\"\">Pixel art</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;- 像素风，复古怀旧的不二之选</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"word-spacing:0.1em;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"border-radius:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;font-weight:bold;background:no-repeat;width:auto;border-width:3px;border-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-style:none;height:auto;\"><span leaf=\"\">Gothic fantasy</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;- 哥特奇幻，华丽阴郁的暗黑美学</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"word-spacing:0.1em;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"border-radius:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;font-weight:bold;background:no-repeat;width:auto;border-width:3px;border-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-style:none;height:auto;\"><span leaf=\"\">Minimalist design</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;- 极简主义，高级感的留白艺术</span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <h4 data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin: 5px 0px;padding: 0px;display: block;text-align: left;font-weight: bold;font-size: 15px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(231, 142, 52);letter-spacing: 0em;text-align: left;font-weight: bold;display: inline-block;\"><span leaf=\"\">5. 材质与特效（细节处的“黑科技”）</span></span></h4>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding:8px 0px;margin:5px 0px;word-spacing:0.1em;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:16px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">细节决定了你的图是“模型”还是“实物”。</span></p>\n   <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;margin: 8px 0px;padding: 0px 0px 0px 20px;color: rgb(231, 142, 52);font-size: 15px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"word-spacing:0.1em;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"border-radius:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;font-weight:bold;background:no-repeat;width:auto;border-width:3px;border-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-style:none;height:auto;\"><span leaf=\"\">Translucent skin</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;- 半透明皮肤，人像写实的终极方案</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"word-spacing:0.1em;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"border-radius:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;font-weight:bold;background:no-repeat;width:auto;border-width:3px;border-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-style:none;height:auto;\"><span leaf=\"\">Iridescent texture</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;- 珠光/彩虹质感，流光溢彩的效果</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"word-spacing:0.1em;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"border-radius:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;font-weight:bold;background:no-repeat;width:auto;border-width:3px;border-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-style:none;height:auto;\"><span leaf=\"\">Metallic sheen</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;- 真实的金属光泽与反射</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"word-spacing:0.1em;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"border-radius:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;font-weight:bold;background:no-repeat;width:auto;border-width:3px;border-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-style:none;height:auto;\"><span leaf=\"\">Porcelain texture</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;- 陶瓷质感，温润细腻的表面</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"word-spacing:0.1em;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"border-radius:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;font-weight:bold;background:no-repeat;width:auto;border-width:3px;border-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-style:none;height:auto;\"><span leaf=\"\">Fluid simulation</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;- 流体模拟，真实捕捉烟雾或水流</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"word-spacing:0.1em;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"border-radius:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;font-weight:bold;background:no-repeat;width:auto;border-width:3px;border-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-style:none;height:auto;\"><span leaf=\"\">Double exposure</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;- 双重曝光，艺术感爆棚的画面融合</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"word-spacing:0.1em;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"border-radius:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;font-weight:bold;background:no-repeat;width:auto;border-width:3px;border-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-style:none;height:auto;\"><span leaf=\"\">Knolling layout</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;- 强迫症平铺排版，产品展示必备</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"word-spacing:0.1em;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"border-radius:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;font-weight:bold;background:no-repeat;width:auto;border-width:3px;border-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-style:none;height:auto;\"><span leaf=\"\">Dispersion effect</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;- 粒子消散效果，动感十足</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"word-spacing:0.1em;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"border-radius:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;font-weight:bold;background:no-repeat;width:auto;border-width:3px;border-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-style:none;height:auto;\"><span leaf=\"\">Chromium finish</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;- 镀铬表面，极强的镜面工业感</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"word-spacing:0.1em;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"border-radius:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;font-weight:bold;background:no-repeat;width:auto;border-width:3px;border-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-style:none;height:auto;\"><span leaf=\"\">Filigree pattern</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;- 繁复的掐丝纹样，增加华丽装饰感</span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <hr style=\"border-radius: 0px;background: linear-gradient(to right, rgba(248, 57, 41, 0), rgb(244, 138, 0), rgba(248, 57, 41, 0)) no-repeat;width: auto;height: 2px;padding: 0px;margin: 20px 0px;border-width: initial;border-style: none;border-color: initial;border-image: initial;text-align: center;\">\n   <h3 data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin: 30px 0px 5px;padding: 0px;display: block;text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;color: rgb(231, 142, 52);letter-spacing: 0em;text-align: left;font-weight: bold;display: inline-block;\"><span leaf=\"\">三、 实战小贴士：如何“组合”这些口令？</span></span></h3>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding:8px 0px;margin:5px 0px;word-spacing:0.1em;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:16px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">指令集不是单纯的堆砌，而是逻辑的组合。一个高阶的 Prompt（提示词）公式通常是：</span></p>\n   <blockquote style=\"margin: 20px 0px;border-style: none none none solid;border-width: 3px 3px 3px 5px;border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) rgb(231, 142, 52);background: rgb(255, 249, 243) no-repeat;width: auto;height: auto;box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px 0px;display: block;overflow: auto;border-radius: 5px;padding: 18px 21px;\">\n    <p style=\"padding:8px 0px;word-spacing:0.1em;margin:0px;text-indent:0em;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"border-radius:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;font-weight:bold;background:no-repeat;width:auto;border-width:3px;border-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-style:none;height:auto;\"><span leaf=\"\">[主体描述] + [环境/构图] + [光影/氛围] + [渲染/材质] + [艺术风格]</span></strong></p>\n   </blockquote>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding:8px 0px;margin:5px 0px;word-spacing:0.1em;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:16px;text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"border-radius:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;font-weight:bold;background:no-repeat;width:auto;border-width:3px;border-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-style:none;height:auto;\"><span leaf=\"\">例如：</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">如果你想画一个穿盔甲的赛博女孩，不要只输入&nbsp;</span><code style=\"letter-spacing: 0em;background: rgb(255, 246, 237) no-repeat;width: auto;height: auto;border-style: none;border-width: 3px;border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0) rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);color: rgb(231, 142, 52);font-size: 15px;overflow-wrap: break-word;padding: 2px 4px;border-radius: 3px;margin: 0px 2px;font-family: &quot;Operator Mono&quot;, Consolas, Monaco, Menlo, monospace;word-break: break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\">cyber girl</span></code><span leaf=\"\">。 尝试输入：</span><code style=\"letter-spacing: 0em;background: rgb(255, 246, 237) no-repeat;width: auto;height: auto;border-style: none;border-width: 3px;border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0) rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);color: rgb(231, 142, 52);font-size: 15px;overflow-wrap: break-word;padding: 2px 4px;border-radius: 3px;margin: 0px 2px;font-family: &quot;Operator Mono&quot;, Consolas, Monaco, Menlo, monospace;word-break: break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\">A beautiful cyber girl wearing futuristic armor, low angle shot, neon ambiance, rim light, highly detailed, octane render, 8k resolution --ar 16:9</span></code></p>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding:8px 0px;margin:5px 0px;word-spacing:0.1em;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:16px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">你会发现，生成的画面瞬间拥有了电影级别的质感！</span></p>\n   <hr style=\"border-radius: 0px;background: linear-gradient(to right, rgba(248, 57, 41, 0), rgb(244, 138, 0), rgba(248, 57, 41, 0)) no-repeat;width: auto;height: 2px;padding: 0px;margin: 20px 0px;border-width: initial;border-style: none;border-color: initial;border-image: initial;text-align: center;\">\n   <h3 data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin: 30px 0px 5px;padding: 0px;display: block;text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;color: rgb(231, 142, 52);letter-spacing: 0em;text-align: left;font-weight: bold;display: inline-block;\"><span leaf=\"\">结语</span></span></h3>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding:8px 0px;margin:5px 0px;word-spacing:0.1em;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:16px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">AI 绘画不是为了取代人类的审美，而是为了缩短“创意”到“现实”的距离。掌握了这些“黑话”，你就拿到了通往新世界大门的钥匙。</span></p>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "文章提供了一套包含光影、画质、构图、风格、材质五个维度的 50 个 AI 绘画核心指令集，帮助用户通过精确 Prompt 创作出高质量作品。",
